# Version control
.git/
.gitignore
.github/

# Python virtual environments & caches
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/env/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/*.egg-info/

# Go build artifacts
**/bin/

# Tests (not needed in production images — CI runs them separately)
**/tests/
**/*_test.go

# Local runtime state
logs/
.pids/
site/
repomix-output.xml

# Secrets & local config
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Editor / OS cruft
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
.DS_Store

# Docs (not needed in runtime images)
docs/
*.md
!README.md

# Node (if ever added)
node_modules/
